Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.61,0:00:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女未满一岁就作为一个超越常人的天才被「设施」所收容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时她才刚刚学会说话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.78,0:00:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里 她认识了「游戏」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.39,0:00:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她玩了许多名为「智能检查」的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.88,0:00:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但对她来说 每个游戏都太无趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.25,0:00:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟谁玩都不觉得有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两年过去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.22,0:00:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女与貌似母亲的女性重逢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个比自己大7岁的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个会精准地附和「大人们」的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.17,0:01:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展现空虚又不具感情的笑容的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.32,0:01:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉默不语的少女 开口说道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.27,0:01:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是…「空空如也」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 我们来玩游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.49,0:01:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『    』…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(410,437)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『    』…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(410,437)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.06,0:01:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『    』…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.06,0:01:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(410,437)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.95,0:02:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是做噩梦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在去拿点热牛奶过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.93,0:02:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥说过 永远都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有温度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人 您在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看您突然飞奔出来 哆啦酱也惊慌失措
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为出什么意外了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉普莉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 有什么吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉普莉尔的主人 是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:02:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何要特意问这个问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:02:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是白大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么跟吉普莉尔较量的是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是白大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要求史蒂芙爱上自己的人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说是白大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现东部联合的游戏内容的人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是白大人和哆啦酱祖父的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吉普莉尔对白大人罕见的才智和谋略衷心钦佩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定终身追随您
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是对白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔奇亚的王「人类种」的全权代理人 白大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(375,437)}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 除了白还有另外一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 没有根据
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城内自然不必说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将打听范围扩大至城市周边 但仍无收获…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 抗议示威游行之中也没有人知道这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕 主人与我们所不知道的人进行游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果败北
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后被篡改了记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会 对手到底是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东部联合…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 他们有可能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来进行游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 赌上主人被植入的虚假的存在进行游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虚假？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我无礼 能请您输给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虚假的存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.05,0:04:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是虚假的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会消失吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.53,0:05:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说人能够改变 真的是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部 全部都会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈祷可以飞翔 就会长出翅膀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得不会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该改变的不是自己 而是方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能去创造
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创造出让没有翅膀的自己能够飞翔的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让白飞起来的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们好好想想吧 不用着急
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部 是虚假的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆全都…消失掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『    』？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(409,437)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『    』…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(409,437)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『    』…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(409,437)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.37,0:06:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『    』没有败北！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.37,0:06:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(348,437)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要赢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空确实存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对…绝对存在！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在 肯定存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您冷静 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从逻辑上考虑…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:06:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确 认为不存在才比较正常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那个人毋容置疑是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.74,0:07:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哆啦酱 你在说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟 白你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能会输呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史蒂芙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 不可能会输
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,造成这种情况的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太感情用事了 应该更…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个 昨天都做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应付游行队伍 然后看到白在王座上玩游戏…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是前天 19号的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前天晚上你们去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是问19号晚的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是确认
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 这是在干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在揉史蒂芙的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我应该做出什么反应才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会兴奋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明让你爱上我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说除了主人外 还有别人要求过哆啦酱爱上他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为提出要求的人是哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 空已经确认存在了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底是为了什么而被揉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谢礼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏史蒂芙 我才能注意到…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么让我们好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空这个人确实存在 那么消失的可能性是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约一天半里 消除我们脑内所有相关记忆的方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用大规模的魔法有可能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话肯定会留下痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:08:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是游戏的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵循盟约的游戏里附加有这种条件的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以全权代理人身份开设的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以影响到全体「人类种」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(532,437)}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是对吉普莉尔就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我现在的身份是侍奉主人的仆从
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应视为我也受此影响
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那究竟是个怎样的游戏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我知道 哥说过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白 我们二人总是一体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥不会扔下白一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白…你在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白…你还在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便哪里都行 能握着我还有感觉的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则我会疯掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绞尽脑汁思考 这种情况…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥所创造的这种情况…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,残留的记忆 全部用上…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥说过 二人为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么哥就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥说过 在游戏开始前就获得胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们因约定而合二为一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥说过 我们不是少年漫画的主人公
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 再仔细想想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更仔细点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥说过 为了得到最后一块拼图
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此而进行的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与东部联合较量所必须的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道具
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监视者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「森精种」？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(408,437)}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了得到「森精种」要怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(408,437)}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向爱尔文·加尔得提出挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 克拉米她不信任哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能答应这种要求…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺取彼此存在…的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白 白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.62,0:11:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺取彼此存在的游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(320,300)\pos(643,339)\an7\3c&H4F0999&\1c&HFFFFFF&\bord2\shad0\fs26\fsp5\be5}解离法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(320,300)\pos(642,319)\an7\3c&H4F0999&\1c&HFFFFFF&\bord2\shad0\fs17\fsp3\be5}Sky Walk
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏是将构成自己存在的三十二种概念设为棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由自己的深层心理反映其优先顺序
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棋子数字越接近「壹」其重要程度越高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 哪颗棋子反映的是自己的哪一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在被对手吃掉之前 反映到现实中为止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己也无法得知
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好比站在你旁边的那位「森精种」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(590,437)}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其手脚 神经 乃至记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后连其存在的痕迹也被抹去成为无法被认知之物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盟约第五条 受挑战的一方有权决定游戏内容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果不愿意的话 那游戏就无法成立
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.83,0:12:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲尔 眼前这个男人已经宣布赌上了「人类种」的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(612,437)}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 还稍微期待过能和解的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和解的话我可以答应哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要相信我 把那边的「森精种」交给我就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(488,437)}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的赌注是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢的人可以要求对方两件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,例如 将游戏的结果永久确定 把对手永远埋葬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.87,0:13:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亦或是篡改对手同伴的一处记忆 将其拉入己方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.75,0:13:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 赌上彼此存在和搭档生杀大权的掠夺游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么在疯狂的同时 顺便再提出一个重要的规则吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉普莉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有何吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:14:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能制作出夺取彼此存在的游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分遗憾 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是像实体化文字接龙那种虚拟世界的话还有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果和「森精种」合作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(424,437)}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合作？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是说跟那群森林里的村野匹夫合作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大战时 被我用「天击」炸飞都城
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.19,0:14:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同垃圾一样般存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并非不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据我所知 那群村野匹夫在编织复杂术式方面颇为擅长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也就是说 空因为进行了这个游戏而消除了自己的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:33.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真如你所说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这种情况是他败北后被消除存在才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是 如果赢了的话 空此刻应该存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说你们的假设都不对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是说游戏仍在进行？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉普莉尔 探测一下这个房间的魔法反应
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白在这个房间醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥和白的寝室明明在不同的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我却在这个房间…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥说过 不会丢下白一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实有施展魔法的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是无法掌握精确的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有尽可能地去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哆啦酱 在空无一物的地方你也能跌倒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.15,0:15:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用再为自己添加角色特点了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跌倒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑白棋的棋子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是「森精种」文字的「3」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(340,437)}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.25,0:15:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么只有棋子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为还尚未使用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算无法认知 也存在于此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 就已知的情况看来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就只有三枚棋子而已啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.06,0:16:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连己方是执黑还是执白都不清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个的话 很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥说过 我们二人为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个游戏 白也参与其中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再提出一个重要的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双方的同伴都可以参加游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在玩家无法继续的情况下 可以接战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我才能留有记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能看见棋盘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我知道哥哥会怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在故意输棋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是哦 我可是在认真地「赢棋」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何诱导对手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你的记忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 故意让我夺走你的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借此证明你并没有任何种族作为后台？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何告知自己的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来他就无法继续游戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 游戏还没结束…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.15,0:17:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 为什么游戏还没宣告终结
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那三枚棋子到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空的哪部分？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何欺骗对手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.25,0:17:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥 太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种方法谁也猜不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有哥和白知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩余棋子里包含的构成哥的要素
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「参」游戏胜利的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.65,0:18:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「贰」对白绝对的信赖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后是「壹」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 你揍我也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经做好觉悟…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该更早一点 更早一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然忘记了主人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.92,0:19:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉米 振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉米 克拉米…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照约定 现在听听我的要求吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.94,0:20:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管要我做什么我都愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但请你放过克拉米…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.49,0:20:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要求一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,固定彼此掠夺的所有记忆 以及归还夺取的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.95,0:20:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保留了从对方那里夺来的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而被夺去的记忆恢复了原状
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样 克拉米和主人了解了彼此的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为了互相信赖的二人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是主人寻找的最后一块拼图
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要求二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的「森精种」 菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(435,437)}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.99,0:20:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要得到篡改你记忆的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个男人的要求是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.61,0:20:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我们做双重间谍对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看过我脑内的记忆后果然与众不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,间谍？是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍后再告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了你脑内的记忆 我改变主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 你可以夸奖我是你引以为傲的哥哥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.57,0:21:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白引以为傲的哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听你这么直白地夸奖 哥会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白 差不多可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备完毕 随时都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超可怕的啊 我再也不做这种事了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.51,0:21:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可怕了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.27,0:22:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这或许也是主人的真实姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.67,0:22:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.57,0:23:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比沙罗曼蛇快多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.16,0:23:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.04,0:23:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,240)\3c&HE1C45B&\shad0\fsp11}请稍作等候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.35,0:23:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长大成人真是悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.00,0:23:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(703,362)\3c&HD000CA&\1c&HFFFFFF&\bord3\shad0\fs33\fsp5\be7}指向法
