Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:41.97,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}空に祈るように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.01,0:23:46.67,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}どうか　永遠に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.21,0:22:43.02,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}承受着无处倾诉的孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.74,0:22:45.49,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}独自哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.54,0:22:53.63,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}无法向他人敞开心扉的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.09,0:22:57.45,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}两人相视而笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.02,0:23:03.64,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}夜已过半 想像深处
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.84,0:23:08.87,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}抛开难以压抑的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.95,0:23:14.53,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}再见 我们必定会重获新生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.62,0:23:18.56,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}挥手告别悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.77,0:23:20.24,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}终有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.33,0:23:22.75,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}为空洞的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.84,0:23:25.60,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}点亮明灯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.28,0:23:31.84,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}将断断续续的话语拼凑合一
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.94,0:23:37.67,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}仅此二人的世界仍将延续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:41.97,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}向天空祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.01,0:23:46.67,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}赐予二人永远
